{
  "page": "Illyrio's manse",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/07/Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png/350px-Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"234\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/07/Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png/525px-Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/07/Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png/700px-Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mariusz_Gandzell_Illyros_estateII.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Illyrio's manse, by Mariusz Gandzel © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Illyrio's manse</b> is the residence belonging to Magister <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> within the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>. It has a view of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bay_of_Pentos\" title=\"Bay of Pentos\">Bay of Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Manse\" title=\"Manse\">manse</a> has brick walls twelve feet high with <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a> spikes atop. There are three gates, the main gatehouse being the chief way in and out of the manse. There is one gate in the <a href=\"/index.php/Garden\" title=\"Garden\">garden</a> that is hidden by ivy. The third gate is a postern by the kennels. The main and postern gates are guarded by some of Illyrio's <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">eunuchs</a>, while the garden gate is chained. The manse has pillared galleries, pointed arches, and a tiled courtyard in which <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion%27s_mushrooms\" title=\"Tyrion&#39;s mushrooms\">mushrooms</a> grow from cracks.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Illyrio decorates one of his bedchambers with soft, patterned <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myrish</a> carpets.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>There is a <a href=\"/index.php/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">marble</a> pool with a statue of a naked youth in its center. The statue is lithe and handsome, made of painted marble so that the hair is blond and shoulder-length. It is poised to duel, with a <a href=\"/index.php/Bravo\" title=\"Bravo\">bravo</a>'s blade in hand.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> According to Illyrio, it was carved when he was sixteen by <a href=\"/index.php/Pytho_Malanon\" title=\"Pytho Malanon\">Pytho Malanon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The pool is surrounded by six cherry trees. The gardens behind the manse are more extensive than the one by the pool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Illyrio serves <a href=\"/index.php/Snail\" title=\"Snail\">snails</a> with garlic from his own gardens.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Illyrio's cellar, long and dim, has barrel-vaulted ceilings and stone walls spotted with nitre. The cellar contains casks of <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a>, including sweet blackberry, sweet reds from the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, sour <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_red\" title=\"Dornish red\">Dornish reds</a>, pale ambers from <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, green nectars and fire wines from <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor_gold\" title=\"Arbor gold\">Arbor gold</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Illyrio also has wines from the <a href=\"/index.php/Further_East\" title=\"Further East\">Further East</a>, including <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Asshai\" title=\"Asshai\">Asshai</a>, as well as <a href=\"/index.php/Strongwine\" title=\"Strongwine\">strongwine</a> from the private stock of <a href=\"/index.php/Runceford_Redwyne\" title=\"Runceford Redwyne\">Runceford Redwyne</a>, a former <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Arbor\" title=\"Lord of the Arbor\">Lord of the Arbor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The manse is guarded by plump <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a>, eunuch soldiers from <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>. Other <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slaves</a> include two fat female cooks, young and old; a potboy; a freckled washerwoman; a <a href=\"/index.php/Girl_bought_to_please_the_king\" title=\"Girl bought to please the king\">blond girl</a> trained in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>; and a mousy older woman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Illyrio reportedly keeps the <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_plague\" title=\"Grey plague\">petrified hands</a> of his second wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Serra\" title=\"Serra\">Serra</a>, in his bedchamber.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/84/Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png/350px-Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"227\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/84/Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png/525px-Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/84/Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png/700px-Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lady_Daenerys%27s_Chambers_FM.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Interior of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>'s chambers, by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> stay at Illyrio's manse in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> for half a year while they await Daenerys's marriage to Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>. Before she is presented to Drogo for the first time, Daenerys is bathed by Illyrio's servants.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a> offers Daenerys the hospitality of his home while she is in <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>. She thinks that Xaro's palace, which appears larger than a market town, makes Illyrio's manse look like a swineherd's hovel.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After crossing the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> is hosted by Illyrio in his manse. He finds clean fine clothes, made for a small boy, in a <a href=\"/index.php/Cedar\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cedar\">cedar</a> chest inlaid with <a href=\"/index.php/Lapis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lapis\">lapis</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mother-of-pearl\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mother-of-pearl\">mother-of-pearl</a>. Tyrion explores the manse until Illyrio convinces him to accompany him to meet some friends to the east. Tyrion takes some <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion%27s_mushrooms\" title=\"Tyrion&#39;s mushrooms\">poisonous mushrooms</a> from the courtyard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>For nigh on half a year, they had lived in the <a href=\"/index.php/Magister\" title=\"Magister\">magister</a>'s house, eating his food, pampered by his servants. Dany was thirteen, old enough to know that such gifts seldom come without their price, here in the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_city\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Free city\">free city</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Tyrion Lannister had lived all his life in a world that was <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">too big for him</a>, but in the manse of <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> the sense of disproportion assumed grotesque dimensions. I am a mouse in a <a href=\"/index.php/Mammoth\" title=\"Mammoth\">mammoth</a>'s lair, he mused, though at least the mammoth keeps a good cellar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>My manse is large enough for any man, and more comfortable than your drafty <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a> castles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D